headline: Medtronic : enrolls first patient in global trial for its Prevail™ drug-coated balloon
summary: Medtronic today announced that the first patient has been enrolled in its pivotal trial of the Prevail™ paclitaxel-coated balloon catheter for in-stent restenosis and de novo small vessel disease....
